      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts as it should, making it a dependable choice for any driver. While the exterior looks great overall, you will find a few minor stone chips on the hood and some light wear on the driver's seat bolster consistent with its age. All electronics are fully functional, and the tires have plenty of tread remaining. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that is ready for the road without needing immediate repairs.",
