    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly collector-grade vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line. This car has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment and has never seen inclement weather. The exterior paint is flawless, treated with a multi-stage ceramic coating that provides a deep, liquid-like luster without a single stone chip or swirl mark in sight. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the upholstery remains supple and matte, the carpets are pristine, and all original factory protective plastics were only recently removed. Every feature, from the panoramic sunroof to the premium infotainment suite, operates with precision. Mechanically, this car is peerless, backed by a folder of documented service records from authorized specialists. It features a spotless undercarriage and a smooth, powerful drivetrain that reflects its low-mileage, enthusiast-owned history. This is an uncompromising choice for the buyer who demands perfection.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
